content: @simulacrum do you know if fetch-latest fetches a database that should work. It seems like the commits in the database fetched through fetch-latest don't contain commits that are in the list of master commits from https://triage.rust-lang.org/bors-commit-list
Ok so seems like perhaps it's completely out of date. I assume triage.rust-lang.org only returns back a limited number of commits and not the entire history, right?
hm, I think the ones that we expect artifacts available for? or maybe since we started collecting
That looks like if the database we fetch using fetch-latest only contains artifacts older than 168 days, we won't find any that exist in that list.
We should really figure out a better way to get those databases out -- exports take forever today
